我用这个让它工作了：
import openai

openai.api_key = &#39;sk-proj-xxx&#39;

completion = openai.chat.completions.create(
model=&quot;gpt-4o&quot;,
messages=[
{&quot;role&quot;: &quot;system&quot;, &quot;content&quot;: &quot;按提示操作&quot;},
{&quot;role&quot;: &quot;user&quot;, &quot;content&quot;: &quot;说，&#39;Hello, World!&#39;}
]
)

print(completion.choices[0].message.content) 

谢谢！
